  "detailed_description": "A Book of Beasts and Buddies is an interactive bestiary of curious creatures. Every page provides an encounter with a mysterious beast for you to befriend.​<br />\r\n<br />\r\nA Book of Beasts and Buddies was designed for the A Game By Its Cover (AGBIC) game jam. The premise of the jam was to design a game based upon a previously existing fictitious game cartridge. A Book of Beasts and Buddies was based upon Bestiary Logbook by Patrick Crotty.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe Audio was done by: Myserval, Dreamreader, and Roni Yosko.",
  "about_the_game": "A Book of Beasts and Buddies is an interactive bestiary of curious creatures. Every page provides an encounter with a mysterious beast for you to befriend.​<br />\r\n<br />\r\nA Book of Beasts and Buddies was designed for the A Game By Its Cover (AGBIC) game jam. The premise of the jam was to design a game based upon a previously existing fictitious game cartridge. A Book of Beasts and Buddies was based upon Bestiary Logbook by Patrick Crotty.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe Audio was done by: Myserval, Dreamreader, and Roni Yosko.",
